channel.title: Deepholz - Techno 128bpm (demo)
channel.description:
Hi there! I‘ve heard so many nice tracks in this forum! And now i want to show you some of mine. I‘m working with auxy since 2 or 3 years. Sometimes more, sometimes less. But this year... it infected me. Finally i played a techno - b2b set with my friend at a small private festival using my ipad and auxy. (Friend laptop + ableton) It was great. I‘m so thankful for this app. Big shoutouts to the devteam!
And now my (work in progress) track:
128bpm https://soundcloud.com/verdattertundzerzausst/deepholz-demo
